Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, come on! You'd better get out of bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's eight! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Why the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the clock wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a high schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on starting school here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join the tennis club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Judo Club's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join the Tea Ceremony Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join the Abacus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.66,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you groaning about, Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Nodoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure which club I should join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You haven't decided on one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been two weeks since school started. You have to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm absolutely terrible at every sport, and I don't really get any of the literary clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how people end up becoming NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pegged as a NEET just 'cause you don't join a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, looking back on it, for as long as I've known you, you've never joined a single club, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Crud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do feel like I ought to at least try to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But what the heck should I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go check out the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Which club do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club! What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was planning on joining the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already filled out the application form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go! Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's disbanded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on the verge of being disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All the students who were in the club last year have now graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so the club will be disbanded unless four students join this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why there wasn't anyone in the Music Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yamanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Yui. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I have a music class to teach in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Music Club, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure was pretty, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand out the syllabus sheets to all the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The syllabus sheets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! So sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.28,Default Over,,0,0,0,,She's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being disbanded, so that's that. I'm gonna go join the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I join and there aren't any members, does that make me the club president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that club you were talking about with those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club is about playing lighthearted music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your plan, Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We wait for prospective members!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I wanted to find out about joining your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm at the Choir Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not join the Light Music Club instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the Choir Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We need more members like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm begging you! You won't regret it, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to force her to join like that! It's really rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that promise we made? Was that just a big lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That I would play drums! And then you would play the bass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our band! We've been saying forever that we would start one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised each other, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That night we went to see that concert together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Were those sweet words nothing but a big lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your flashback is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are going to play in a band together! Is that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You forced the idea on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you said you wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we went pro, we said we'd split all the proceeds 70/30!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a great deal of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The only instrument I can play is the keyboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like to join your club if you'll have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! Now we only need one more person to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose that means I'm already a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi Kotobuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ritsu Tainaka, drums. This is Mio Akiyama, she's on bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Now we need a guitar player!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My high school years are very important. I wanna do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have absolutely no idea what it is I should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like any french fries with that, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I would love some. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time eating in a fast food restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's silly but I've always dreamed of having someone ask me if I wanted french fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Please begin the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay, this meeting's come to order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to recruit one more member by the end of the month!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're meeting to think of a way right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, offering people an amazing prize if they decide to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,An amazing prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like some kind of gift or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a car or a plane or a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing but impractical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,More along the lines of ice cream or help with homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would join up for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyororin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The president shouldn't lose interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up with something to keep me interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, for now, why don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... there's just one more week remaining in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's answered our ads yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Disbanded before we are a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Light Music, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, my click, clack, click, clack, here, ha, hi, is a click...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very good at that, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being, I have decided to join the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? So, what is it that they do at this club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But since the name of the club is "light music," I figured they only do really easy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know like whistling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like they don't have much ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? It looks like they're some kind of band.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But I don't know how to play the guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, what can you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play castanets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, click, fu, clack, fu, click...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a perfect fit for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look at this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.55,Default Over,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.92,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A prospective member has come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Isn't that wonderful news?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Also that's a lovely tea set, but make sure you clean up after yourselves once you're done, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.70,Default Over,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now we won't be disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui Hirasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just her name makes her sound really awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to be a guitarist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A real powerhouse has joined us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Light music club...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Light music club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get down this hallway, I won't reach the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club is up in the Music Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be an easy thing to say right after joining, but I've got to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of people would join a Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to quit, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could walk away without any consequences?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!\NYou've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's the useless clumsy bad tempo girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Yui Hirasawa by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who wants to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I misjudged you! I'm sure you must be totally awesome on guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all been waiting for you to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like someone's been embellishing things about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Our brand-new member has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.40,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good to have you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Mugi, go get the tea ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, it's quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should give up on trying to quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind music do you like to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your all time favorite band?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which guitarists do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... I have to tell them. I can't really play the guitar at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,J...{\c&HBD8755&} J... J...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say Jimi Hendrix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not. I mean, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy Page, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Oh, no, I ju... ju...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.14,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeff Beck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there really this many guitarists whose names start with "J"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, Jeff Beck, that's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In the music world, they say that there's only two kind of rock guitarists: Jeff Beck, and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a brilliant and challenging guitarist who's always searching for new sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so hardcore, Miss Hirasawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta say I'm so glad that someone like her joined the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We were at the point where the club would have been disbanded if we hadn't gotten another member within the next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for joining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep making it harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm... I'm just going to have to spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, I don't know how to say it if I made a mistake joining this club but I only came here to beg you to let me quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be playing a different kind of instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What instrument can you play, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Casta... Er, the harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have a harmonica right here. Try playing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Miss Hirasawa, if you wanted to join this club, that means that you're at least interested in music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there another club you'd rather join?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, none in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let this mark leave this room no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep the club from being disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to keep her here somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I really mean it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have cookies and madeleines as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.36,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're baiting the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So good... I-I'm sorry, I didn't mean to come here and gorge myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should start eating snacks like this every day from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we drifting off topic here... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hirasawa, what other sorts of things do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I like anything that tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, just food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On your days off, do you spend your time at home doing anything in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sitting around, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like cute things, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very good with extreme heat or cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I spend winter under the table where it's warm. And in the summer, I spend my time on the floor where it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't go, I'm begging you! You can just hang out and do nothing if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to bring even tastier snacks, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take things seriously when I applied to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I got all your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I ever apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have tried to force you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So please! At least hang around for a while and listen to us play a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll play a song for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's swallowed the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard to put into words!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't very good, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seemed like it would be a whole lot of fun to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that I'm going to join this club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's commemorate the start of the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But the problem is that I can't play any instruments at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be a manager or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we aren't a sports club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, why don't you take this opportunity to begin learning the guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks very complicated! I don't think I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the three of us, we'll teach you everything you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to you play just now made me feel like I can do at least that well, if not a lot better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So glad to be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You went ahead and joined anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They practically begged me to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, as a manager or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone else says it, it sounds insulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined as a full-fledged member of the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say they'll teach me to play guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that means you're gonna have to go out and buy yourself a new guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll let me borrow one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy them for about $50, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. I wonder if the Light Music Club knows what they're getting themselves into with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone! These three are my fellow Light Music Club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to pick a club where I could make friends with sort of fun, pleasant people that one so rarely meets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I finally made it to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've joined a club for the first time!
